description: 2013-2014 strategic plan for the  Department of Military and Veterans Affairs  five major program areas associated with its divisions. There are three under the division of the National Guard, and one each for the Civil Air Patrol and the Department of Veterans Affairs. These are National Guard Federal, National Guard State, National Guard Family, Civil Air Patrol, and Veterans Affairs.
